{"tid":2147149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打銀行CEO：香港聯繫匯率制「無懈可擊」","createTime":"2020-08-09T05:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T08:38:06.000Z","uid":91914,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f330dadea17f17bb327527da1f7b65d266f1b3","tid":2147149,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"財經頻道／綜合報導〕香港近日成為美中衝突下的熱點，從去年香港反送中抗爭，到今年中國實施香港版國安法，外界都持續猜測，美國有可能以破壞美元、港元聯繫匯率制度為手段制裁中國，但渣打銀行執行長Bill Winters最新表示，出於港幣有龐大的外匯存底，香港的聯繫匯率制可說是「無懈可擊」（unassailable）。<br />\n《彭博》報導，渣打銀行執行長Winters今（30）稱，美元、港元聯繫匯率制度受到香港貨幣儲備非常穩固的支持，若企圖削弱香港，恐怕會在更大範圍上，對金融體系造成相當有害的影響，且在當前疫情大流行的狀況下，很難理解世界上的任何決策者會認為，破壞聯繫匯率制是一件好事。<br />\n而如渣打銀行和匯豐銀行，均將香港視為其最大市場，且是香港3大發鈔銀行中的兩家。<br />\n不過，美國知名金融大鱷巴斯（Kyle Bass）已在今年5月成立新基金，以200倍權權槓桿做空港幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3244948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3244948&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminDrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=70b7a560\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3244948</a>"},{"pid":"f6cd86626603eb10934ef3d604959a07f50a4039","tid":2147149,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaf58f3eb2744d81cddad874a840cdaf9d24b95","tid":2147149,"uid":82640,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"渣打曾因向受制裁人士提供服務而被罰11億美元<br />\n渣打講嘢可唔可信大家自己判斷"},{"pid":"b44cc63f4a882e883647dcd14818b2e99dd53220","tid":2147149,"ui